WEBVTT

00:01.197 --> 00:02.117
<b>Upsy-daisy.</b>

00:03.587 --> 00:06.347
<b>Uh, keys, keys...</b>

00:06.347 --> 00:08.117
<b>There we go.</b>

00:15.357 --> 00:16.707
<b>Up we go.</b>

00:20.147 --> 00:21.547
<b>Whoa! Ugh!</b>

00:26.587 --> 00:28.437
<b>Man...</b>

00:31.047 --> 00:32.967
<b>There we go.</b>

00:44.877 --> 00:46.577
<b>That's off.</b>

00:48.847 --> 00:50.397
<b>And the other.</b>

01:58.577 --> 02:01.567
<b>Ah, delish!</b>

02:02.477 --> 02:04.057
<b>Huh?</b>

02:04.057 --> 02:08.887
<b>Oh, yeah, was I supposed to ask Makima something?</b>

02:10.537 --> 02:12.037
<b>Meh, whatever.</b>

02:13.777 --> 02:15.457
<b>Huh?</b>

02:16.557 --> 02:19.207
<b>Water. Water.</b>

02:54.867 --> 02:56.517
<b>Oh?</b>

02:56.517 --> 02:58.817
<b>Den-Den-Denji?</b>

02:59.327 --> 03:02.047
<b>What are you doing at my place?</b>

03:02.737 --> 03:06.927
<b>Oh, did I bring you here?</b>

03:08.157 --> 03:09.427
<b>Huh?</b>

03:09.887 --> 03:11.867
<b>My head is spinning.</b>

03:11.867 --> 03:13.177
<b>What the hell?</b>

03:15.377 --> 03:20.447
<b>So, you're in love with Makima, aren't you?</b>

03:21.307 --> 03:22.817
<b>My head is spinning.</b>

03:23.567 --> 03:26.887
<b>Give up on that bitch.</b>

03:26.887 --> 03:27.917
<b>Geez.</b>

03:27.917 --> 03:29.337
<b>Aki should, too.</b>

03:29.337 --> 03:31.657
<b>He's so lovestruck.</b>

03:32.257 --> 03:33.987
<b>Geez!</b>

03:33.987 --> 03:36.337
<b>Geez! Horndogs!{she's actually punning on "moo" being like a cow's mooing}</b>

04:09.197 --> 04:10.237
<b>Wanna do it?{implying sex, I guess}</b>

04:18.507 --> 04:22.117
<b>D-Do what?</b>

04:24.447 --> 04:25.997
<b>Sexual intercourse.</b>

04:30.927 --> 04:31.667
<b>Arms up!</b>

04:41.637 --> 04:42.517
<b>Okay.</b>

04:43.477 --> 04:44.527
<b>Good boy.</b>

04:44.527 --> 04:46.017
<b><i>Should I do it?</i></b>

04:46.807 --> 04:47.637
<b>Good boy.</b>

04:47.637 --> 04:50.607
<b><i>My first kiss was supposed to be with Makima.</i></b>

04:50.607 --> 04:51.487
<b>Good boy.</b>

04:51.487 --> 04:53.607
<b><i>But this woman tainted it with puke.</i></b>

04:54.307 --> 04:56.897
<b><i>Do I really want my first time to be with her?</i></b>

05:01.407 --> 05:02.557
<b>Yes!</b>

05:10.207 --> 05:11.897
<b>There, there.</b>

05:14.327 --> 05:16.757
<b>Let's take off everything down here, too.</b>

05:26.707 --> 05:27.497
<b>Oh?</b>

05:28.817 --> 05:29.777
<b>Huh?</b>

05:30.267 --> 05:33.267
<b>There's something in your pocket.{Or is Denji just happy to be here}</b>

05:36.087 --> 05:38.037
<b>A Chupa Chups?</b>

05:38.037 --> 05:38.817
<b>That's so gross.</b>

05:39.177 --> 05:39.847
<b>Ah!</b>

05:40.637 --> 05:43.327
<b>Denji. Denji!</b>

05:43.827 --> 05:46.897
<b>Denji, are you okay?</b>

05:46.897 --> 05:48.777
<b>Let's get you some fresh air.</b>

