06:59.017 --> 07:02.317
<b>So here, your first indirect kiss</b>

07:03.177 --> 07:05.517
<b>tastes like cola-flavored Chupa Chups.</b>

07:13.067 --> 07:14.837
<b>Sorry, Pochita.</b>

07:15.367 --> 07:17.397
<b>You wanted to have sex too, right?</b>

07:17.887 --> 07:21.917
<b>But I want my first time to be with Makima.</b>

07:23.117 --> 07:25.637
<b>So first, I have to kill the Gun Devil.</b>

07:26.937 --> 07:28.687
<b>Then...</b>

07:37.167 --> 07:38.197
<b>Denji.</b>

07:38.197 --> 07:39.107
<b>Good morning.</b>

07:43.037 --> 07:45.157
<b>Do you feel like breakfast?</b>

07:50.177 --> 07:53.167
<b>Food tastes great when
 you're looking down at people, huh?</b>

07:53.907 --> 07:55.037
<b>Denji,</b>

07:55.837 --> 07:59.987
<b>I was drunk last night and don't remember anything.</b>

08:00.647 --> 08:02.917
<b>Could it be that I forced myself on you?</b>

08:02.917 --> 08:05.547
<b>Like I'd do it with a puke-woman like you!</b>

08:05.547 --> 08:08.247
<b>Plus, I'm set on my first time being with Makima.</b>

08:10.577 --> 08:12.837
<b>Oh, that's good. I'm relieved.</b>

08:12.837 --> 08:16.807
<b>I'd get arrested if I'd seduced a minor.</b>

08:26.817 --> 08:29.477
<b>You're pretty unusual, Denji.</b>

08:29.477 --> 08:32.997
<b>A normal person would feel awkward
 and leave right away.</b>

08:32.997 --> 08:34.567
<b>Huh?!</b>

08:34.567 --> 08:37.037
<b>Why would I leave if I can have free food?</b>

08:38.887 --> 08:41.297
<b>So, do you love Makima?</b>

08:41.687 --> 08:42.667
<b>Super love her!</b>

08:43.807 --> 08:46.547
<b>Even if her personality turns out to be shit?</b>

08:46.547 --> 08:47.547
<b>Love her a shitload!</b>

08:52.017 --> 08:53.287
<b>Right!</b>

08:53.287 --> 08:56.267
<b>Then how about I help you two get together?</b>

08:56.267 --> 08:58.347
<b>What?! Seriously? Wow!</b>

08:58.667 --> 08:59.897
<b>Totally serious.</b>

08:59.897 --> 09:03.527
<b>Okay, Denji, let's form a super-secret alliance.</b>

09:04.127 --> 09:07.127
<b>I'll help you get together with Makima,</b>

09:07.127 --> 09:09.047
<b>and you help me get together with Aki.</b>

09:17.857 --> 09:19.247
<b>What do you even like about him?</b>

09:19.247 --> 09:20.247
<b>His face.</b>

09:21.077 --> 09:22.447
<b>I see.</b>

09:23.727 --> 09:25.677
<b>Alright! I'm in!</b>

09:26.237 --> 09:28.047
<b>Alliance formed!</b>

09:28.897 --> 09:34.467
<b>Alright, then from today on, let's treat each other
 as friends, rather than senior and junior colleagues.</b>

09:39.577 --> 09:41.757
<b>Come over for breakfast once in a while.</b>

09:41.757 --> 09:43.867
<b>And bring fiend-girl and Aki with you.</b>

09:50.267 --> 09:52.647
<b>Wonder if we can get Makima to come, too.</b>

10:05.297 --> 10:07.547
<b>What time do we arrive in Kyoto, again?</b>

10:08.307 --> 10:10.377
<b>In about 30 minutes.</b>

10:10.377 --> 10:11.967
<b>Let's get station lunches, then.</b>

10:12.647 --> 10:14.707
<b>You have a work lunch at 1 p.m.</b>

10:14.707 --> 10:17.597
<b>Don't worry, I'll be hungry again by then.</b>

10:19.277 --> 10:22.927
<b>I'm not very excited to talk to the Kyoto big shots.</b>

10:22.927 --> 10:24.517
<b>They're all pretty scary.</b>

10:25.067 --> 10:28.307
<b>And I prefer eating in a peaceful environment.</b>

10:30.117 --> 10:33.617
<b>The booze last night was so good.</b>

11:08.717 --> 11:11.017
<b>This is Team C. I repeat, Team C.</b>

11:11.017 --> 11:11.927
<b>Commence.</b>

