20:27.797 --> 20:30.547
And yet, here I am, still live and kicking.

20:27.797 --> 20:30.547
It's thanks to my partner Aki being a really

20:27.797 --> 20:30.547
stand-up guy. I'm not too worried about him.

20:27.797 --> 20:30.547
The other day everyone at work got dead drunk

20:27.797 --> 20:30.547
and was passed out, and I woke up at some

20:27.797 --> 20:30.547
point and thought I'd be nice and go buy water

20:27.797 --> 20:30.547
for everyone for when they got up.

20:27.797 --> 20:30.547
Then I realized we'd forced Aki into getting his

20:27.797 --> 20:30.547
ears pierced. Why, you may ask? Because we

20:27.797 --> 20:30.547
always get dead drunk. He looked really

20:27.797 --> 20:30.547
distressed about it. And he got angry when I

20:27.797 --> 20:30.547
told him I didn't remember it happening.

20:27.797 --> 20:30.547
He was really exasperated, but it actually

20:27.797 --> 20:30.547
 looked pretty good on him.

